Package: bdlR
Title: Query the GUS Bank Danych Lokalnych (BDL) Local Data Store
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Felix", "Beilin", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "fbeilin@princeton.edu")
Description: Provides a convenient interface for querying a local Parquet/DuckDB
    store of data scraped from the Polish Central Statistical Office (GUS)
    Bank Danych Lokalnych (BDL) API. Supports filtering by variable, subject
    category, geographic level, year, and administrative unit.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Imports:
    DBI,
    duckdb
